                    </div>

                    <div class="col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
                        <div class="icon-box">
                            <i class="bi bi-house-check"></i>
                            <h3>New Developments</h3>
                            <p>
                                We have successfully worked on new building developments, delivering clean, professional finishes.
                            </p>
